com.hp.ov.sdk.dto.storage

Class StoragePool

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hp.ov.sdk.dto.BaseModelResource
      • com.hp.ov.sdk.dto.storage.StoragePool
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class StoragePool
extends BaseModelResource
    The StoragePool data transfer object (DTO) contains the information used to represent a storage pool in the system. It is passed in to the add/update storage pool REST api, as well as the add/update storage pool through java client api.
